    <string name="help_bookview">"In this screen you can see the detailed information of the selected book.
        \n - Tap ‘read’ or ‘unread’ to mark the book accordingly.
        \n - Tap the star rating to set or modify the book rating.
        \n - Tap the check icon, top right of the screen, near help, to save changes to the book (read status and rating).
        \n - Tap the delete button, bottom right of the screen to delete the book."</string>
    <string name="help_addbook">"In this screen you can choose to add a new book by isbn number or to enter the fields manually.
        \n - Introduce a valid ISBN number and press add to search the book by isbn.
        \n - Tap enter the book manually to proceed to enter the book fields manually.
        \n - Note that the isbn search is provided by a 3dr party and can be Inaccurate."</string>
    <string name="help_addbookform">"In this screen you can see the info provided by the isbn number or enter a new book manually.
        \n - Title, Author, Category are required fields
        \n - Tap the check icon, top right of the screen, near help, to save the new book.</string>
    <string name="help_help">"In the main screen you can see a list of books, to add more books, press the plus button bottom right of the screen.
        \n You can search the list of books with the search icon in the taskbar and choose between different search methods in the menu behind search.
        \n On the slide menu, you can choose between tree different order methods to display the main list."</string>
